Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.41,0:02:07.35,Sign,,0,0,0,,Vienna
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be late for work, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I'm not in Munich!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.20,0:02:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I now live with dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So refreshing! \NFeels good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, let's make the best of this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.80,0:03:00.27,Sign,,0,0,0,,Kärntner Ring Atelier
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, I know you've been working till wee hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.26,0:03:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now, I'm making you a breakfast, \Nso, would you rather scrambled eggs, or boiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.38,0:03:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate boiled eggs...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.45,0:03:23.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, scrambled it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home soon, lest it goes cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.77,0:03:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this Luise, so early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.36,0:03:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise is making breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.46,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.08,0:03:50.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Resi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.86,0:03:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Fraulein...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:58.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Resi, could you take the juice out of the fridge?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.86,0:04:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,And put that bread in the basket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.38,0:04:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,How is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.19,0:04:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning, Peperl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.58,0:04:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I actually made a proper breakfast for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it must be that the end of times is already near. {herald; harbinger; forerunner; portent; sign; omen of natural disaster; cataclysm​}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.83,0:04:14.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraulein Luise is cooking!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.84,0:04:18.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.11,0:04:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you cut your fingers somewhere? Any burns? \NHow many times did you drop the pot? {/turned over}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.10,0:04:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it hurt anywhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.48,0:04:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing of the kind.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.96,0:04:28.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.96,0:04:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, Peperl.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,It's going cold. Hurry up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.40,0:04:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.53,0:04:44.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.62,0:04:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Glad to know. It's the first time I'm cooking at home, \Nso I was morbidly nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.87,0:04:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, you don't eat while standing. {/you should sit on the stool}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.47,0:04:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.04,0:04:57.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Manners, cooking...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.11,0:05:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I never had any idea you know words like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Herr Master, this must be a divine miracle!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.67,0:05:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? What's so miraculous in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.74,0:05:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a little something I picked up in summer camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.74,0:05:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This, too, because of summer camp?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.34,0:05:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Well I'll be, this summer camp \Nsounds like an excellent place!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.33,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Great!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.80,0:05:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.05,0:05:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my, I was counting on Lotte to wake me up as usual, \Nbut something went wrong...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.47,0:05:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte. Lotte, what's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.94,0:05:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not feeling quite well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me sleep, I don't care!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.42,0:05:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay. I can see now you are quite fine and well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.30,0:05:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! But nothing's fine about this! \NYou'll be late for school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.02,0:05:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,School only starts tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.61,0:05:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me be, Resi. {/sleep}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Resi?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.20,0:05:57.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! I am in Munich now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. Who is that Resi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is... The girl that used to wake me up \Nevery morning in summer camp.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,So I mistook you for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.52,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's relieving. You almost had me scared \Nthat you're feverish or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:13.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, but that's for later! \NI'm late now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.93,0:06:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.43,0:06:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be more careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.49,0:06:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, mom has to go out now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.59,0:06:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope I'm not too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom, should I cook you something today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Please do. I'll try my best to finish the work sooner, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.55,0:06:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.05,0:06:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,My first attempt at cooking. \NGotta give it my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.95,0:06:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And mom's favorite dish is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.64,0:06:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Beef soup with macaroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.73,0:06:46.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Buy the beef at Huber's Butchery, \Ncorner of Prince Eugene Straße.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.55,0:06:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Eugene Straße...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,This here is Prince Eugene Straße.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Butchery on the corner...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.66,0:07:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.95,0:07:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. Welcome back, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Back from vacations?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:06.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Tomorrow, I go to school again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.30,0:07:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But today, I need to make mom a dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A beef soup with macaroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.25,0:07:12.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. As usual, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:13.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.55,0:07:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, half-pound of filet with marbling,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.39,0:07:17.89,Sign,,0,0,0,,"Half-pound of filet with marbling..."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:18.99,Default,,0,0,0,,also a kidney and some marrowbones...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.99,0:07:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you covered, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.72,0:07:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the best, Herr!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.55,0:07:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the wait, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.46,0:07:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Herr. {/uncle?}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Neither mom nor the old Herr have had a single clue \Nthat I'm actually Luise. All according to plan! {/perfect}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.71,0:07:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,And the next stop is, \NFrau Wagenthaler's grocery store - {(someone's) wife} {from de}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.66,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,there, buy vegetables and macaroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.37,0:07:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, stop for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.28,0:07:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you do your homework even in the street now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know vacation isn't over yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who could this girl be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.97,0:08:05.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you know people look strange at you for that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.84,0:08:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Need to change the subject, let's see... {to evade (a question, taxes, etc.); to dodge; to gloss over (a mistake, fault, etc.); to smooth over; to get one's way out of (a difficult situation); to explain away​}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.60,0:08:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna come with me? \NI'm going to get some vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's the meaning...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.08,0:08:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.64,0:08:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to bring me along for some shopping?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.17,0:08:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I would like some carrots, potato, \Nand some broccoli, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.52,0:08:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,My, that's a rare sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.29,0:08:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie and Lotte together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This is pointless. {absurd; ridiculous; silly; ludicrous; nonsensical; asinine; foolish}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.39,0:08:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm leaving!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.73,0:08:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,She said, "Annie." \NThat's who you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.02,0:08:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.89,0:08:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Annie Habersetzer. {half en half de}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.87,0:08:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We go to the same class, \Nbut this girl is a huge thorn in my side!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of her, some girls in the class, \Nespecially the smallest one - Ilse Merck - are crying daily! {half en half de} {tiny; little; wee}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But nobody dares to fight her off, \Nbecause she'll come back for you later. {lit: payback; tit for tat; retaliation; revenge is scary, so nobody to go against; to oppose; to disobey; to defy - maybe they're afraid to fight back, maybe they're afraid of revenge, idk}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,How interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave me alone, Annie!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.08,0:08:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ilse Merck, didn't you just try to run away \Nas soon as you noticed me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.51,0:09:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I never did!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, speak of the devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.36,0:09:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Do you mean to declare \Nyou just disregarded me on purpose? {/didn't notice me}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you harass Ilse, Annie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.35,0:09:09.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me, Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.43,0:09:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? Our perpetually voiceless Herrin Lotte \Nis suddenly feeling valiant? {brave; valiant; gallant; courageous}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.20,0:09:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Harassing the weak - \Nhow come you yourself don't find it shameful?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What the dickens? \NYou think you can lecture me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.59,0:09:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Who'd do such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.08,0:09:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.25,0:09:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Lotte slapped Annie! {she doesnt say slapped but w/e}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.51,0:09:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time you try to bully Ilse, \Nremember that I coming for you! {/I won't forgive you}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.68,0:09:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Ilse.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.06,0:09:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, you'll regret this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.21,0:09:48.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Young Fraulein, please don't do this to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.37,0:09:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're leaving me completely out of work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.57,0:09:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. I always wanted to try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.66,0:09:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not dreaming, are we, Herr Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.55,0:09:56.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, whatever is happening, it's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.48,0:10:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, \Nwhere did you get that apron?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.04,0:10:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Apron...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.96,0:10:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.31,0:10:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend from the summer camp gifted me one. \NPretty, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.62,0:10:14.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time I'm seeing you wearing an apron, \Nbut it looks becoming already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.76,0:10:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Except mom bought it for me as a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.87,0:10:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, I will, unfortunately, have to leave you for now. \NI have a meeting at Opera House.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.71,0:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,But in the evening, \Nyou join Herr Strobl to come see the opera.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.50,0:10:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.97,0:10:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, see you in the evening. {/I'm off}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:28.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:40.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do it, Peperl. While dad is away in the Opera House, \Nwe'll pay a secret visit to his world of inspiration! {/workshop}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.89,0:10:49.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here is St. Stephen's Cathedral.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.43,0:10:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"You turn left after passing by the Opera House \Nand find yourself on Kärntner Ring."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:10:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the place!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.42,0:11:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Astounding!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.02,0:11:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you even manage to clutter a place this much? {/how did he manage to make it so messy}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Peperl, I have a confession for your ears only. {to confide; to reveal; to disclose; to lay bare; to speak frankly; to open (one's heart)}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm actually not Luise.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.48,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise is my twin sister, \Nand I am Lotte, the other one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But make sure you don't spill it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And in exchange, I'll be keeping you \Non a tasty breakfast diet, from now on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.19,0:11:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.15,0:11:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,So, let's seal our friendship with an oath. {sign/mark/token - the same as before}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then Peperl, \Nwe've got some cleaning to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.61,0:12:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll help me, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.25,0:12:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise, this is your dress. \NFirst time I'm wearing something this elegant.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.04,0:12:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Young Fraulein! Herr Strobl had arrived to pick you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.45,0:12:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My, that's a sight to behold.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody in the world would say \Nyou don't look like the most proper lady, Luise.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.93,0:12:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been some time since I wore this. \NIt's a little embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.60,0:12:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, it looks strikingly becoming on you, Young Fraulein.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.05,0:12:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if dad notices this dress, \Nif I wave my hand to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.62,0:12:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Have no doubt in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In all those years, the one thing that remained unaltered \Nis your dad noticing you, wherever you may be. {/until now there's not been a single time when he didn't notice you}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,With that said, will you allow me \Nto escort you to the destination, Young Fraulein?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.19,0:12:59.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I kindly hope you do, Herr Strobl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.59,0:13:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear, this girl is a polar opposite \Nof our usual Luise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a safe trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.73,0:13:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,But really, her being that docile is uncanny, even. \NAnd she left me with a whole lot of nothing to do! {/she became so quiet/docilea} {lit: I couldn't have made it any easier/for me too, can't be easy; simple; without trouble; without hardships - unsure if she means "louise will now be more harsh and demanding, so my work becomes harder" or "she makes my work incredibly easy"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.23,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's hope it's not forever. {again unsure, "if it goes on until when"}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.48,0:13:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see. The cook book is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.98,0:13:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.01,0:13:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If I follow this, I've naught to fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.92,0:13:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,And so, beef soup with macaroni...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.62,0:13:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"First, you boil some water \Nand cook the meat until it's soft. {/until it becomes tender}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.23,0:13:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,In the meantime, you boil macaroni\Nwith a spoonful of salt." {/one pinch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.90,0:13:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all? Piece of cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.10,0:13:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we make soup by boiling the meat. {/for soup, we put in ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.13,0:13:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.93,0:13:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"In the meantime - macaroni.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.01,0:13:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Add a spoonful of salt." {/one pinch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.72,0:13:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do I know which spoon they used? {/how much is one pinch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just say, "moderate amount." {/whatever, I'll just add what amount I see fit} {suitable; proper; appropriate; adequate; fit; fair​}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.22,0:14:00.41,Default,,0,0,0,,"In the pot with the meat, \Ngrate a nutmeg with a grater."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.41,0:14:02.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But where might the grater be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.05,0:14:02.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.65,0:14:06.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.52,0:14:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.85,0:14:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,What was it... "To make sure the meat is soft enough, \Ntry piercing it with a fork."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No! I haven't found the grater yet. {/before that, ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.97,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! And what are all those vegetables for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.46,0:14:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad, the vegetables belong in the soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I must wash them and put in the soup, \Nfirst and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.68,0:14:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Nutmeg was also there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Now it's all wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.39,0:14:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,But either way, into the meat pot you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.69,0:14:35.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But wait! I was supposed to grate it first! {/I haven't found the grater}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, whatever. \NWon't make any difference in the stomach. {/they'll enter the ... together}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.79,0:14:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The water is overflowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.63,0:14:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,So many plates are in pieces.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.60,0:14:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,To top it off, I'm soaking wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This Onion is so evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.01,0:15:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why am I crying that hard? \NWhat's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"When the meat is soft enough, remove it from the pot. \NAnd take out the bones with a colander." {doesn't make any practica; sense, but that's what she says}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.76,0:15:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Half of the soup is now on the floor!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't be helped. \NWill have to refill it with water. {/add}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.65,0:15:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, I made it through, somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get a little taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.02,0:15:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! {/bad/disgusting}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.88,0:15:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom would refuse flatly to eat something like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.84,0:15:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems, I won't ever be able \Nto make a convincing Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.15,0:15:40.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.25,0:15:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I gotta hurry if I'm to do it before mom returns!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,We made a rule against it, \Nbut it's my last resort measure! {/it's against the rules, but I can't help it}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.39,0:15:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need a little guidance on seasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.26,0:15:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.09,0:15:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.34,0:15:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? Is that you, Fraulein Luise?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.57,0:16:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm not. \NBut is Fraulein Luise currently out? {/not there}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.87,0:16:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, our Fraulein won't be home until the night, Ma'am. {/is now out}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.48,0:16:08.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well. Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gosh... Just where could Lotte have gone off to? \NAnd at such a crucial time, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.24,0:16:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Magnificent, dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.26,0:16:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The best in Vienna... \NNo! The best in the whole world artist!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.87,0:17:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so out out patience for when he looks over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.15,0:17:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And for his secret signal, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.91,0:17:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,A gorgeous Frau, isn't she? {/beautiful lady}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.98,0:17:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my, it seems, she is also a friend of your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Want some?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.04,0:17:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No thank you. {/I'm good}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.74,0:18:18.78,Sign,,0,0,0,,What shall I do without Eurydice? {Che farò senza Euridice?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.61,Sign,,0,0,0,,Where shall I go... {Dove andrò senza il mio ben?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.45,0:18:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte's dinner, which dish might it be, \Nafter such a long break?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.02,0:18:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't wait to find out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.54,0:18:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm back, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.52,0:18:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Nobody's waiting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.68,0:18:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.92,0:18:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.34,0:18:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.30,0:18:55.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, will you tell me what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:19:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry mom. \NYou return home to such a disarray. {/I made the whole house dirty} {"Mommy, don't be angry! I think I've unlearned how to\Ncook.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.59,0:19:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the apron you bought me last year is soiled... {unsure she means this, she doesn't say what happens to the apron}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay, Lotte.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.47,0:19:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing simpler \Nthan washing a dirty piece of cloth. {/if you wash something dirty, it'll become clean}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you mad at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.41,0:19:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I destroyed the meat and the plates...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I was more worried that {\i1}you{\i0} may be mad at me. {/the one who should receive the anger is me}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.83,0:19:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I had overburdened you \Nwith all the housework there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.85,0:19:25.54,Default,,0,0,0,,But the way I bungled mom's favorite \Nbeef soup with macaroni is beyond salvation... {/I ruined/made a mistake}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,To bungle something so spectacularly \Ntakes a true artist, Lotte. {/blunder/mistake that beautiful is a work of art}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.03,0:19:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"Together with mom, eventually, \Nwe made our whole flat shine again. {/entire house clean}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.21,0:19:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, starting from scratch \Nwe prepared another beef soup with macaroni. {/remade}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,The soup that I cooked together with mom \Nhas been the tastiest ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.56,0:19:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I even regretted I can't let Lotte taste it, too. I really did. {/wanted to treat lotte to it too}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.70,0:20:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom has been the most understanding, \Nas though we've known each other for eternity. {/has been getting along for whole life}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I pray that Lotte, too \Nstays on the best possible terms with dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.04,0:20:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,From Munich."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.11,0:20:10.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to see some good dreams tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.02,0:20:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The opera has been gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.93,0:20:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so anxious to not miss a single second of it, \NI even came an hour too soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.27,0:20:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's flattering.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering if you would allow me \Nto take a look at your atelier. {to stop by (while on one's way to another place); to drop by; to make a short visit}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.75,0:20:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? Sure. Just be prepared it's a little messy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.95,0:20:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Truly sorry for the mess, but please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Which part of it do you consider a mess? {/wher's the mess}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.53,0:20:58.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right, it's actually a pretty tidy place.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.14,0:21:05.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Among those who have the keys... {/could enter this room}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.26,0:21:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise cleaned it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.18,0:21:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That woman... \NI wonder if she and dad are close friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.91,0:21:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Luise, it seems, I'm about to lose \Nanother night's sleep to worries. {/seeds of anxiety have been sown again}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.77,0:21:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Munich and Vienna -
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.54,0:21:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it appears, both those worlds \Nhave been shaken to the core by this day. {idfk what he means, fukeru/fuku has a ton of meaning none of which make sense}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.28,0:21:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet, with the fall of night, \NLotte and Luise - just two little girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.18,0:21:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,gently tuck away the happiness in their hearts{ for later}, \Nmerely breathing out a sigh of relief. {lit: delights and sighs/exhales, softly; gently; quietly; lightly​ to wrap up, it seems - I've never yet been so lost as to what he means}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.54,0:23:22.94,Sign,,0,0,0,,In the next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.41,0:23:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,We two have swapped places!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.82,0:23:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Lotte, I made a big fuss \Nin a school I've never attended before.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.45,0:23:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Did you give away our secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.15,0:23:38.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Not {\i1}that{\i0} big! But still, I've had enough \Nof Annie bullying the weak, so I introduced her to my palm.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.06,0:23:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God, Luise, why can't you ever control your urges?
